/*!
  \page ARM ARM

<h2>Software dependencies</h2>

In order to build the code for the Marvell 88MW300 SoC download this SDK;

<ul type="disc">
  <li>git clone https://github.com/marvell-iot/aws_starter_sdk.git</li>
</ul>

Follow these <a href="https://github.com/marvell-iot/aws_starter_sdk/wiki">instructions</a> on how to build and deploy the hello world application.

<ul type="disc">
  <li>https://github.com/marvell-iot/aws_starter_sdk/wiki</li>
</ul>

In order to build the documentation <a href="http://www.stack.nl/~dimitri/doxygen/">doxygen</a> is required.

<ul type="disc">
  <li>http://www.stack.nl/~dimitri/doxygen</li>
</ul>


<h2>Build Instructions</h2>

<p>In the defconfig file set the path to the Marvell SDK.</p>

Set cross compile option in defconfig
<ul type="disc">
  <li>CONFIG_ARM=y</li>
</ul>

<ul type="disc">
  <li>make</li>
</ul>

*/

/*!
  \page linux Linux

<h2>Software dependencies</h2>

The GCC toolchain is required

In order to build the documentation <a href="http://www.stack.nl/~dimitri/doxygen/">doxygen</a> is required.

<ul type="disc">
  <li>http://www.stack.nl/~dimitri/doxygen</li>
</ul>

<h2>Build Instructions</h2>

Turn off cross compile option in defconfig
<ul type="disc">
  <li>CONFIG_ARM=n</li>
</ul>

<ul type="disc">
  <li>make</li>
</ul>

